title: Queensryche - Hammersmith Odeon 1990-11-15 Complete
description:
Queensryche
Live At Hammersmith Odeon 11/15/90

This is the complete show (minus the dialogue) from Hammersmith that was included on the bonus discs of the Operation: Mindcrime and Empire Deluxe 2CD sets. Unlike the bonus discs, this is in the proper running order, and unlike the Operation: Livecrime expansion I posted earlier, this is the entire show, one that contains Hand on Heart instead of The Lady Wore Black. I thought this would go over well here, because these are very difficult to find lossless.
